𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐒𝐭𝐮𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐥 𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐨𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐄𝐗𝐓𝐄𝐍𝐃𝐄𝐃! ⏳

Still thinking about stepping up? This is your chance to be part of the team that leads with heart, serves with a smile, and empowers the ITHM community. 

Don’t miss out on this opportunity to grow, lead, and shine!
Be the smile. Be the voice. Be the next ITHM Student Leader.
